nitf
Class FileSecurity

java.lang.Object
  nitf.NITFObject
      nitf.FileSecurity

public final class FileSecurity
extends NITFObject

A representation of the NITF security information. This information differs between the NITF specification versions, but this class represents the information as a whole. Each component that has security information makes reference to a FileSecurity object.
